<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-32-1093 </DOCNO><TEXT>The use of computing power to control and advance the functionality ofthe existing subsystems in the home is a new, infant industry. The term&quot;Home Automation&quot; is commonly used to describe this emerging industry.This paper will review the status of home automation, explain why homeautomation products are needed, describe some examples of consumer benefits,outline how the products are likely to evolve, and comment on why itmatters to demand-side management. 3 figs.</TEXT></DOC>